'''霍利斯特'''（{{lang-en|'''Hollister Co.'''}}，通常稱為「Hollister」或「HCO」），是[[美國|美國]] [[Abercrombie_&_Fitch|Abercrombie & Fitch]](A&F) 旗下的[[服飾|服飾]]品牌。主要以南加州衝浪氛圍來呈現整體商品的風格與形象，相較於A&F，HCO走的是相對[[平價|平價]]的路線<ref name="piperjune">{{cite web |url=http://library.corporate-ir.net/library/61/617/61701/items/249197/Piper_June_2007.pdf |title=Four Iconic Businesses: One "BRAND" |format=PDF |accessdate=2008-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120105115444/http://library.corporate-ir.net/library/61/617/61701/items/249197/Piper_June_2007.pdf |archive-date=2012-01-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="ANFCareers">[http://www.abercrombie.com/anf/hr/jobs/careers.html A&F Careers] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080708185600/http://www.abercrombie.com/anf/hr/jobs/careers.html |date=2008-07-08 }}</ref>。2019年派傑投資公司({{link-en|Piper Sandler Companies|Piper Jaffray}})將其列為青少年服裝品牌前五名<ref name=piperjaffreay>{{cite press release | title = Taking Stock With Teens - Fall 2019 Infographic | publisher = {{link-en|Piper Jaffray|Piper Jaffray}} | date = 2020-02-18 | url = https://www.pipersandler.com/2col.aspx?id=5752}}</ref>，該品牌以實體[[店面|店面]]及[[網路商店|網路商店]]來進行[[銷售|銷售]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollisterco.com/hol/homepage.html|title=Hollister Co. Official Website|publisher=Abercrombie & Fitch, Inc.|accessdate=2013-07-26|archive-date=2019-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190717052542/https://www.hollisterco.com/hol/homepage.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://library.corporate-ir.net/library/61/617/61701/items//anf_.pdf|format=PDF|title=Four Iconic Brands, One Aspiration}}{{dead link|date=March 2011}}</ref>。

